  <section>
    <title></title>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Access
    Mailbox</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>You can access your mailbox from:</para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Your own extension:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Dial the internal Listen voicemail number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your passcode and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Someone else's extension:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Dial the internal Listen voicemail number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>*</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your mailbox number and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your passcode and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>An external phone:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Dial the external Listen voicemail number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>*</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your mailbox number and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your passcode and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Mailbox
    Menu</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>This menu is accessed upon entering your mailbox.</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>The following options are available:</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to retrieve a
            message.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to send a message to
            another mailbox.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis> for mailbox
            maintenance.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press<emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>8</guilabel></emphasis>
            to dial a number</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>9</guilabel></emphasis> for paging
            support</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis> when finish.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Listen to
    Messages</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Access mailbox.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to
        retrieve messages.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>The current message count is played (<emphasis># of new and old
        messages</emphasis>).</para>

        <para>Messages are played in the following order:</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>New messages only</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>New and old messages - Each new message is played, followed
            by the old messages.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Old messages only</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>No messages - A message is played stating that there are no
            messages and you are returned to the Mailbox Menu.</para>

            <para><emphasis>Note: The order that the messages are played in
            (newest to oldest or oldest to newest) is based on the
            subscriber's settings.</emphasis></para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>The first message is played followed by the Message Menu
        options.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to go to the next
            message.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to pause the
            message.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis> to delete the
            message.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>4</guilabel></emphasis> to skip
            backward</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>5</guilabel></emphasis> to save the
            message.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>6</guilabel></emphasis> to skip
            forward.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>7</guilabel></emphasis> to repeat the
            message.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>8</guilabel></emphasis> to reply to
            sender.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>9</guilabel></emphasis> to restart from the
            beginning of all messages.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>0</guilabel></emphasis> to forward the
            message to another mailbox</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>*</guilabel></emphasis> to replay the menu
            options.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis> when finished. The
            Mailbox Menu option is played again.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>If no option is selected, the current message is
            replayed.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>The next message is played followed by the Message Menu options.
        This continues until all messages (<emphasis>new and old</emphasis>)
        have been played.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Once all messages have played, you are returned to the Mailbox
        Menu.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Reply to
    Sender</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Access Mailbox.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to
        retrieve messages.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>After the message you wish to reply to is played, press
        <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>8</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to dial the caller's
            number</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to leave a voice
            message</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>to return to the
            previous menu</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Record your message.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis> or
        hang up.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Forward
    Message</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Access Mailbox.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to
        retrieve messages.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>After the message you wish to forward is played, press <emphasis
        role="bold"><guilabel>0</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the mailbox number you wish to forward the message
        to.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>A message is played indicating the message was
            forwarded.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>The Message Menu is played.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Mailbox Maintenance
    Menu</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>This menu is accessed by pressing <emphasis
    role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis> from the Mailbox
    Menu.</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>The following options are available:</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to change your
            mailbox greeting.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to change your
            passcode.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press any other key to return to the previous menu.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Change
    Greeting</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Access mailbox.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis>
        for mailbox maintenance.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to
        change your mailbox greeting.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis> to return to the
            previous menu.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press any other key when you hear the number with the
            greeting you wish to change.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Each mailbox number is played.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>If no number is selected, you are returned to the Mailbox
            Maintenance Menu.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press any key when you hear the number of the greeting you wish
        to change.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Record your message and press <emphasis
        role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis> to complete the
        recording.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>The Record Menu options are played.</para>

            <itemizedlist>
              <listitem>
                <para>Press <emphasis
                role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to save.</para>
              </listitem>

              <listitem>
                <para>Press <emphasis
                role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to listen to the
                recording.</para>
              </listitem>

              <listitem>
                <para>Press <emphasis
                role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis> to
                re-record.</para>
              </listitem>

              <listitem>
                <para>Press <emphasis
                role="bold"><guilabel>4</guilabel></emphasis> to return to the
                previous menu.</para>
              </listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to
        save the greeting and return to the Mailbox Maintenance Menu.</para>

        <para>OR</para>

        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to
        listen to the greeting and then press 1 to save the greeting and
        return to the Mailbox Maintenance Menu.</para>

        <para>OR</para>

        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis> to
        re-record the message. Record the message and press 1 to save the
        greeting and return to the Mailbox Maintenance Menu.</para>

        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>4</guilabel></emphasis> to
        return to the previous menu without changing your greeting.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>At the Mailbox Maintenance Menu, press any key (<emphasis>except
        1 and 2</emphasis>) to return to the Mailbox Menu.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Change
    Passcode</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Access mailbox.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis>
        for mailbox maintenance.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Press <emphasis role="bold"><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to
        change your passcode.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the new passcode and press <emphasis
        role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Re-enter the new passcode and press <emphasis
        role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>The passcode is saved and you are returned to the Mailbox
        Maintenance Menu.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>At the Mailbox Maintenance Menu, press any key (<emphasis>except
        1 and 2</emphasis>) to return to the Mailbox Menu.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>For More
    Information</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>See the Listen User's Guide for additional information and advanced
    features.</para>
  </section>
